    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488490/extras/648354b4af4b32937ad86d327a442409.poster.avif?t=1762191298\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488490/extras/648354b4af4b32937ad86d327a442409.webm?t=1762191298\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488490/extras/648354b4af4b32937ad86d327a442409.mp4?t=1762191298\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>欢迎光临尼瓦里斯！在这座赛博朋克城市中，想要获得成功并非易事。黑社会想摘走你的身体器官，统治集团甚至会对公民的呼吸收罚款。与此同时，城市的地基正摇摇欲坠，没准明天就会沉没于大海，所以必须把握当下，争取尽早发财。<br> <br>成功都是从小生意起步——小吃摊、面店或者兴奋剂店，然后会升级至酒吧、餐厅或者夜总会，直到最高级别,掌控尼瓦里斯的夜生活，那时候你将是这里的夜晚之王！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488490/extras/a60af828fbf6fae4e201e7edde452fc9.poster.avif?t=1762191298\" width=620 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488490/extras/a60af828fbf6fae4e201e7edde452fc9.webm?t=1762191298\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488490/extras/a60af828fbf6fae4e201e7edde452fc9.mp4?t=1762191298\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>这是一款与众不同的模拟游戏，天气与昼夜交替效果非常逼真。你可以自主选择如何在尼瓦里斯度过时光，创业经商、完成各种奇怪的任务、或是结交朋友。体验这座三维赛博朋克城市的危险与奇妙。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>模拟你在尼瓦利斯的生活，决定自己每一天的生活方式。<br></li><li>管理你的事业，包括餐馆、拉面摊和夜总会。<br></li><li>购买或自己生产食材。<br></li><li>开发与众不同的菜品，调配别有风味的鸡尾酒，吸引合适的顾客光临。<br></li><li>乘着自己的小船探索这座城市，顺便钓钓鱼。<br></li><li>布置自己的房子，或者买一套新房重新装修。<br></li><li>了解陌生人、朋友和顾客的故事，也许还会找到真爱。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488490/extras/559ccaf0e91cc7ec75808a70878a3ea5.poster.avif?t=1762191298\" width=620 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488490/extras/559ccaf0e91cc7ec75808a70878a3ea5.webm?t=1762191298\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488490/extras/559ccaf0e91cc7ec75808a70878a3ea5.mp4?t=1762191298\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
